name: FNF Imposter V3 Test
description:
It's Imposter V3 from Week "Imposter" Friday Night Funkin Vs. Imposter V3! Play as Credits do really go to Clowfoe for making the Friday Night Funkin Vs. Imposter V3 mod :) ! Play on the web here on a PC/Mobile devices! If you want, if you have a windows computer, you can also download it with the download button below!

Controls: 

To switch to touch control, touch the toggle in game.

Arrow keys to play the sounds (For mobile press D-pad button) 

Secret Key = ??? ;)

Hold any of the buttons to hold a pose!

Check out the Friday Night Funkin here: https://ninja-muffin24.itch.io/funkin

Also check out Friday Night Funkin on Newgrounds: https://www.newgrounds.com/portal/view/770371
